Colour. Head and pronotum black with greenish lustre. Palpi and antennae brown, gradually lighter apically. Labrum black with yellow borders. Elytra dark reddish brown with dark metallic lustre, especially along lateral margin and suture (
Fig. 8
). Epipleura red. Legs with brownish black tibiae, femora red with dark apex, tarsomeres red with somewhat darker apex.
